<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-black dark:text-white p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8 rounded-lg">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
      <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> L'<strong>indicativo</strong> è il modo della certezza. Indica azioni che sono accadute, che accadono o che accadranno. È formato da:
    </p>
    <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 ml-6">
      <p><span class="text-red-500">•</span> <strong>quattro tempi semplici</strong> → presente, imperfetto, passato remoto, futuro semplice;</p>
      <p><span class="text-blue-500">•</span> <strong>quattro tempi composti</strong> → passato prossimo, trapassato prossimo, trapassato remoto, futuro anteriore.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
      Osserva lo schema del modo indicativo e completa le frasi coniugando il verbo <strong>suonare</strong> al tempo indicato.
    </h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full border-collapse text-sm md:text-base">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-100 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/50">
            <th class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 font-bold">Tempi semplici</th>
            <th class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 font-bold">Tempi composti</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 mb-2">Presente</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                <span>Io</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="suono" data-correct-answer="suono">
                <span>il campanello.</span>
              </div>
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2">Passato prossimo</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                <span>Io</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="ho suonato" data-correct-answer="ho suonato">
                <span>il campanello.</span>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/20">
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 mb-2">Imperfetto</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                <span>Io</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="suonavo" data-correct-answer="suonavo">
                <span>il campanello.</span>
              </div>
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2">Trapassato prossimo</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                <span>Io</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="avevo suonato" data-correct-answer="avevo suonato">
                <span>il campanello.</span>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 mb-2">Passato remoto</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                <span>Io</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="suonai" data-correct-answer="suonai">
                <span>il campanello.</span>
              </div>
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2">Trapassato remoto</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                <span>Io</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="ebbi suonato" data-correct-answer="ebbi suonato">
                <span>il campanello.</span>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/20">
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 mb-2">Futuro semplice</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                <span>Io</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="suonerò" data-correct-answer="suonerò">
                <span>il campanello.</span>
              </div>
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-4">
              <p class="font-semibold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 mb-2">Futuro anteriore</p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                <span>Io</span>
                <input type="text" class="w-32 border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 dark:text-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="avrò suonato" data-correct-answer="avrò suonato">
                <span>il campanello.</span>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2: Underline simple and compound tenses -->
  <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="true">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
      Sottolinea tempi semplici<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-red-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="red" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span> e tempi composti<span class="inline-block w-5 h-5 bg-blue-300 rounded ml-1 cursor-pointer" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span>.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Tra pochi minuti <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">usciremo</span> tutti dallo spogliatoio.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">Era stata</span> una notte durissima a causa del temporale.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Quando <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">ascolto</span> questa musica, <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">sono</span> felice!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">Avevo invitato</span> Michela a casa mia, ma <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">ha detto</span> di no.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 dark:bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-900/30 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Dopo che <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">avrò parlato</span> con Bea, ti <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">dirò</span> che cosa <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="red">penso</span>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-right text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
    Esercizi pp. <%= link_to "164", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p164"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %>, <%= link_to "165", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p165"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %> e <%= link_to "169", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p169"), class: "text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-200 underline" %>
  </div>

  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
</div>
